@@ -0,0 +1,20 @@
+# Github stats collector
+
+Info about commit 
+`https://api.github.com/repos/{Owner}/{repo}/commits/{sha}`
+
+```txt
+
+a=0
+d=0
+t=0
+
+for i in json['files']:
+    a += i['additions']
+    d += i['deletions']
+    t += i['changes']
+a = additions
+d = deletions
+t = total lines changed
+
+```
\ No newline at end of file
